Package com.esri.gpt.control.harvest Description

Harvest controller. Provides functionality to control various processes associated with harvesting module. Allows to create, and modify harvest repositories, extracts harvest history with harvest reports, implements endpoints for Harvesting Tool, and Harvesting Service.
